WEBVTT

00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:01.901
The Department will provide a current,

00:00:01.968 --> 00:00:05.205
accurate copy of an Employee's position description to the

00:00:05.271 --> 00:00:08.007
Employee at the time of his or her assignment,

00:00:08.074 --> 00:00:12.512
when changes are made, and when the Employee requests a copy.

00:00:12.579 --> 00:00:16.983
The Department will also provide a current copy to the Union upon request.


